Template License Notice

This repository currently ships with a placeholder license notice.

Copyright (c) 2026 The repository owner.
All rights reserved.

Why this file is a placeholder:

1. This repository is being productized as a reusable Git template.
2. The final legal owner and distribution model may differ for each consumer.
3. A template should not silently imply an open-source license that has not been approved.

Before external distribution, open-source publication, or commercial release, replace this file with the final license approved for your organization and update the related project metadata and documentation.
